      "widgets_values": ["Professional fashion lookbook video generated from the reference image.\n\nThe model remains completely still in the same pose as the reference image.\nThe body posture and gaze direction never change. Only the camera positions change.\n\nThe exact same outfit must remain identical in every shot.\nNo garment redesign and no color changes.\n\nThe video lasts 5 seconds total with hard cuts between shots.\nEach shot uses a different STATIC camera placed around the model.\nCameras do not move. No zoom. No push-in. No orbit.\n\nShot 1 (0-1s): Frontal full-body hero shot. Face visible. Identity established.\nShot 2 (1-2s): Camera at chest height on top garment. Face cropped out.\nShot 3 (2-3s): Low camera near floor on trousers and shoes. Face not visible.\nShot 4 (3-4s): Rear-side camera at 120 degrees. Back silhouette. Face not visible.\nShot 5 (4-5s): High camera looking down at torso texture. Face cropped out.\n\nLIGHTING: Clean editorial studio, identical across all shots.\nNo face visible after shot 1. No artifacts. No flicker."],
      "title": "📝 Video Prompt (5 shots)"
    },
